#Mythic Feats
Drink Is Life					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																													PRESTAT:1,CON=19				PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,3																																				DESC:Strong drink fuels the mythic fires within you.																																																																																																																																																																								BENEFIT:You never take penalties for consuming nonmagical alcohol, and you can consume an alcoholic beverage as a swift action instead of a move action. Each time you consume an alcoholic beverage, you may gain one of the benefits of polypurpose panacea. You can have only one of these benefits active at a time. If you expend one use of mythic power while drinking an alcoholic beverage, you can heal 2 points of ability damage, negate a temporary penalty to one ability score, or remove one of the following conditions: confused, diseased, exhausted, fatigued, frightened, nauseated, poisoned, shaken, sickened, or staggered.	INFO:Prerequisite|Con 19, 3rd mythic tier.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Drink Is Life	SOURCEPAGE:p.63
Dual Path						CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																																			PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You follow two mythic paths.																																																																																																																																																												BENEFIT:Select a mythic path other than the path you selected at your moment of ascension. You gain that path's 1st-tier ability (either archmage arcana, champion's strike, divine surge, guardian's call, marshal's order, or trickster attack). Each time you gain a path ability, you can select that path ability from either path's list or the list of universal path abilities.	INFO:Prerequisite|1st mythic tier.	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Mythic Path / Second|1	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Dual Path	SOURCEPAGE:p.63
Extra Mythic Power				CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																																			PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You can store more mythic power than your tier would normally allow.																																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|MythicPowerTimes|2																																																BENEFIT:You gain two extra uses of mythic power each day.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Extra Mythic Power	SOURCEPAGE:p.65
Extra Path Ability				CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																																			PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,3																																				DESC:You can call upon mythic powers beyond those already invested in you.																																						BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Mythic Path Ability|1																																																																																																																														BENEFIT:Choose one mythic ability from your path or from the universal path abilities that you meet the prerequisites for. You gain that path ability.	INFO:Prerequisite|3rd mythic tier.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Extra Path Ability	SOURCEPAGE:p.65
Fabulous Figments					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Spell Focus (Illusion)																										PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your illusions are astonishingly realistic.																																																																																																																																																																						BENEFIT:Non-mythic creatures can't identify your illusion spells with Spellcraft, including checks attempted as part of arcane sight, detect magic, or similar effects. When mythic creatures attempt to identify your illusions, add your tier to the DC of those Spellcraft checks. Mythic creatures informed by their allies that one of your illusions isn't real gain only a +2 bonus on their Will saves to disbelieve. Non-mythic creatures gain no bonus to disbelieve.	INFO:Prerequisite|Spell Focus (illusion).	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Fabulous Figments	SOURCEPAGE:p.65
