Legendary Teamwork				CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,TYPE=Teamwork																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You and your allies fight with great coordination.																																																																																																																																																																					BENEFIT:Any fixed numeric bonuses you gain from teamwork feats are increased by 1. This doesn't apply to variable numeric bonuses or to effects that are not numeric bonuses, such as additional attacks of opportunity, movement, or other extra actions.	INFO:Prerequisite|Any two teamwork feats.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Legendary Teamwork	SOURCEPAGE:p.68
Lucky Surge						CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Mythic Feat,Potent Surge																										PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,3																																				DESC:Your surges defy the odds.																																																																																																																																																																							BENEFIT:Whenever you use your surge ability, you can roll your surge dice twice and take the higher result. If you can already roll your surge dice twice and take the higher result, you roll your surge dice three times and take the highest result.	INFO:Prerequisite|Potent Surge, 3rd mythic tier.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Lucky Surge	SOURCEPAGE:p.68
Maximize Surge					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																																			PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,6																																				DESC:In times of dire need, you can burn your mythic power to ensure success.																	STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE																																																																																																																																																BENEFIT:Once per day when you surge, you can expend two uses of mythic power to treat your surge die as though it rolled the maximum result.	INFO:Special|You can take this feat multiple times. Each time you do, you gain an extra use of this feat per day.	INFO:Prerequisite|6th mythic tier.		DEFINE:Feat_MaximizeSurge_Times|0	BONUS:VAR|Feat_MaximizeSurge_Times|1	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|Feat_MaximizeSurge_Times	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Maximize Surge	SOURCEPAGE:p.69
Mythic Paragon					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																																			PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your mythic power is even more potent than that of most other mythic beings.																																																																																																																																																															BENEFIT:Your tier is considered 2 higher for determining the potency of mythic abilities, feats, and spells. This doesn't grant you access to mythic abilities or greater versions of mythic spells at a lower tier than you would normally need to be to get them, nor does it grant you additional uses of mythic power or adjust the dice you roll for your surge.	DEFINE:MythicLevel|0	BONUS:VAR|MythicLevel|2	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Mythic Paragon	SOURCEPAGE:p.70
Mythic Spell Lore					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																						PRESPELLCAST:TYPE=Arcane,TYPE=Divine							PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You have learned how to unlock the power of your spells, combining them with your mythic power.																	STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE												BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Mythic Spells|MythicTierLevel																																																																																																																													BENEFIT:You can learn a number of mythic spells equal to your tier and can expend mythic power when casting them to enhance the results. To select a mythic spell, you must be able to cast the non-mythic version or have it on your list of spells known. Every time you gain a new tier, you can select an additional mythic spell.	INFO:Special|You can select this feat multiple times. Each time you select this feat, you must select different spells.	INFO:Prerequisite|Ability to cast spells.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Mythic Spell Lore	SOURCEPAGE:p.70
Potent Surge					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic																																			PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your surge is more potent.	BENEFIT:Whenever you use your surge ability, add 1 to your surge result.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Potent Surge	SOURCEPAGE:p.71
Titan Strike					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Mythic Feat,Improved Unarmed Strike																								PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your fists can fell titanic foes.																																												BONUS:WEAPONPROF=Unarmed Strike|DAMAGESIZE|1																																																																																																																		BENEFIT:Your unarmed strike deals damage as if you were one size category larger. You also gain a +1 bonus for each size category that your target is larger than you on the following: bull rush, drag, grapple, overrun, sunder, and trip combat maneuver checks and the DC of your Stunning Fist.	INFO:Prerequisite|Improved Unarmed Strike (mythic).	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Titan Strike	SOURCEPAGE:p.75
Two-Fisted Drinker				CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Quick Draw																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You can pound down drinks with amazing verve.																																																																																																																																																																		BENEFIT:You can draw two potions or other beverages--mundane or magical--from a pouch, bandolier, or similar holder (but not from a backpack) as a move action. As a standard action, you can drink two potions or other beverages. You must have two free hands to use this feat.	INFO:Prerequisite|Quick Draw.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Two-Fisted Drinker	SOURCEPAGE:p.76
Valiant Vault					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Mounted Combat,Ride-By Attack									PRESKILL:1,Ride=5														PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your mount can make heroic leaps.	BENEFIT:Your mount is always considered to have a running start when using Acrobatics to jump. You can expend one use of mythic power to grant your mount a +10 bonus on an Acrobatics check, or a +20 bonus if the check is made to jump.&nl;When making a mounted charge, you can guide your mount to leap over a foe between your starting position and the target of your charge. You make a Ride check or your mount makes an Acrobatics check (whichever is lower) during the charge, using the rules for the leap task under the Ride skill. If the height you clear with that check exceeds the creature's height, you jump over it and continue your charge on the opposite side. This movement provokes attacks of opportunity. Alternatively, you can vault over your target while making a Ride-By Attack, allowing you to move over or through its space and continue moving on the opposite side of it. If your jump exceeds the target's height, you gain a +1 bonus on the attack roll for higher ground, and if any of your allies threatens the target, you treat the target as flanked for purposes of your Ride-By Attack.	INFO:Prerequisite|Mounted Combat, Ride-By Attack, Ride 5 ranks.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Valiant Vault	SOURCEPAGE:p.76


