Selective Channeling (Mythic)		KEY:Selective Channeling				CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Selective Channeling																											PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:When you exclude creatures from your channel, you empower those you do affect.																																																																																																																																																																		BENEFIT:When you channel energy, the damage you heal or deal increases by a number of points equal to twice the number of targets you excluded from your channeled energy. You can expend one use of mythic power to increase the number of targets you exclude from your channeled energy by %1.|HalfMythicLevel	INFO:Prerequisite|Selective Channeling.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Selective Channeling	SOURCEPAGE:p.72
Self-Sufficient (Mythic)		KEY:Self-Sufficient					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Self-Sufficient																											PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Independence comes naturally to you, and you have mastered taking care of yourself.																																																																																																																																																										BENEFIT:The bonus on Heal and Survival skill checks from Self-Sufficient increases by 2. In addition, you can expend one use of mythic power to treat a Heal or Survival check as if you had rolled a natural 20. You must decide to use this ability before making the roll.	INFO:Prerequisite|Self-Sufficient.	BONUS:SKILL|Heal,Survival|2	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Self-Sufficient	BONUS:SKILL|Heal,Survival|2	SOURCEPAGE:p.72
Shatter Defenses (Mythic)		KEY:Shatter Defenses					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Shatter Defenses																											PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your dazzling attacks leave your opponents flummoxed and bewildered, unable to attack you or to defend themselves effectively.																																																																																																																																																																									BENEFIT:An opponent you affect with Shatter Defenses is flat-footed to all attacks, not just yours.	INFO:Prerequisite|Shatter Defenses.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Shatter Defenses	SOURCEPAGE:p.72
Shield Focus (Mythic)			KEY:Shield Focus					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Shield Focus																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You're a master of using your shield for protection.																																																																																																																																																																					BENEFIT:Add your shield bonus and your shield's enhancement bonus to your touch AC. As an immediate action, you can expend one use of mythic power to add your shield bonus and your shield's enhancement bonus on a Fortitude or Reflex save just before you roll it.	INFO:Prerequisite|Shield Focus.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Shield Focus	DEFINE:ShieldAddsToTouchAC|0	BONUS:VAR|ShieldAddsToTouchAC|1|TYPE=Boolean	SOURCEPAGE:p.73
Shield Slam (Mythic)			KEY:Shield Slam						CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Shield Slam																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your shield bash produces a powerful kick.																																																																																																																																																																				BENEFIT:When using Shield Slam to bull rush, an opponent knocked prone because of an intervening wall or other surface also takes damage from the collision. The damage dealt is equal to %1d6 points. As an immediate action, you can expend one use of mythic power to add +%2 to your combat maneuver checks when resolving a bull rush made due to Shield Slam.|HalfMythicLevel|MythicLevel	INFO:Prerequisite|Shield Slam.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Shield Slam	SOURCEPAGE:p.73
Shot on the Run (Mythic)		KEY:Shot on the Run					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Shot on the Run																											PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:With ease, you can snap off two shots while dashing across the battlefield.																																																																																																																																																																							BENEFIT:Whenever you use Shot on the Run, you can make two ranged attacks at your highest base attack bonus at any point during your movement, instead of just one.	INFO:Prerequisite|Shot on the Run, base attack bonus +6.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Shot on the Run	PREATT:6	SOURCEPAGE:p.73
Skill Focus (Mythic)			KEY:Skill Focus						CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Skill Focus																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You mastery with this skill is unmatched, even in difficult situations.																STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:ABILITYSELECTION|FEAT|Skill Focus																																																																																																																																												BENEFIT:You can always take 10 or 20 on checks with your choice of skill for Skill Focus, even when you are rushed or threatened.	INFO:Special|You can gain this feat multiple times. The effects do not stack. Each time you take this feat, it applies to a different non-mythic Skill Focus feat.	INFO:Prerequisite|Skill Focus.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Skill Focus	SOURCEPAGE:p.73
Snatch Arrows (Mythic)			KEY:Snatch Arrows					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Snatch Arrows																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You can use the weapons you pluck from the air to immediately make melee attacks.																																																																																																																																																																				BENEFIT:When you use Snatch Arrows to catch a thrown weapon that can also be used as a melee weapon, you can make a melee attack with it as an immediate action against a foe within the weapon's melee reach. You can expend one use of mythic power to make this attack without spending an immediate action.	INFO:Prerequisite|Snatch Arrows.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Snatch Arrows	SOURCEPAGE:p.74
Sociable (Mythic)				KEY:Sociable						CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Sociable																													PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your easy nature flows from you without effort, putting others at ease.																																																																																																	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|2																																																														BENEFIT:You grant and benefit from the +2 bonus on Diplomacy checks from Sociable constantly without having to spend a move action. You can spend a move action to increase the bonus to +4 for %1 rounds.|MythicLevel	INFO:Prerequisite|Sociable.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Sociable	SOURCEPAGE:p.74
Spell Focus (Mythic)			KEY:Spell Focus						CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Spell Focus																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your magical specialties are particularly effective.																STACK:NO	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SCHOOLS|ABILITY=FEAT[Spell Focus]																																																																																																																																												BENEFIT:Choose a school of magic you already have Spell Focus in. The bonus to save DCs provided by Spell Focus and Greater Spell Focus for that school increases by 1. You can expend one use of mythic power as part of casting a spell from your chosen school to force any of the spell's targets to roll their saving throws twice, taking the lower result.	INFO:Special|You can gain this feat multiple times. The effects do not stack. Each time you take this feat, it applies to a different non-mythic Spell Focus feat.	INFO:Prerequisite|Spell Focus.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Spell Focus	BONUS:DC|SCHOOL.%LIST|1|TYPE=MythicSpellFocus	SOURCEPAGE:p.74
Spell Mastery (Mythic)			KEY:Spell Mastery					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Spell Mastery																												PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:You're so familiar with certain spells you can prepare them with the greatest of ease.																																																																																																																																																																							BENEFIT:You can prepare spells you have selected with Spell Mastery as a full-round action. You must spend the appropriate amount of time preparing other spells you have not mastered. As a full-round action, you can expend one use of mythic power to prepare all your spells that you have selected with Spell Mastery.	INFO:Prerequisite|Spell Mastery.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Spell Mastery	SOURCEPAGE:p.74
