Two-Weapon Rend (Mythic)		KEY:Two-Weapon Rend					CATEGORY:Mythic Feat		TYPE:Mythic	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Two-Weapon Rend																											PREVARGTEQ:MythicTierLevel,1																																				DESC:Your synchronized dual attacks are even more dangerous, and can leave lasting wounds.																																																																																																																																																																					BENEFIT:The damage of your Two-Weapon Rend increases to 2d8 points plus %1. You can expend one use of mythic power to gain a %2 bonus on this damage.|2*STR|2*MythicLevel	INFO:Prerequisite|Two-Weapon Rend.	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mythic Feat Output ~ Two-Weapon Rend	SOURCEPAGE:p.76
